RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: Sentinel-1 RTC VV dB Stretch
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: Sentinel-1 RTC VV data in dB scale with a Stretch applied

Function.Name: Stretch
Function.Description: Enhances an image by adjusting the range of values displayed. This does not alter the underlying pixel values. If a pixel has a value outside of the specified range, it will appear as either the minimum or maximum value.

AnyType.Name: Sentinel-1 RTC VV dB
AnyType.Description: Sentinel-1 RTC VV data in dB scale

Function.Name: Calculator
Function.Description: Computes a raster from a raster based mathematical expression.

Argument.Name: Sentinel-1 RTC VV Power
Argument.Description: This raster function extracts the VV band (band 1). Values are in power scale.

Function.Name: Extract VV Band
Function.Description: Specifies that band 1 is the VV band in the composite rasters.

AnyType.Help: Values are converted from power to dB scale.

RasterFunctionTemplate.Help: Values are converted from power to dB scale, and a Min-Max stretch is applied to visualize well by default.
